      "content": "a warm compress isn't really gonna help this much, i think it's more like a nerve or bone thing. i'm just so desperate to get some sleep. i feel like i could handle a bit more than just heat. if i took like another 800mg of the ibuprofen right now, would that actually kill me or is it just about the stomach stuff? i just need to know if i can push through it.",
